data.name: Gravekeeper's Visionary
data.desc: You can Tribute Summon this card by Tributing 1 "Gravekeeper's" monster. This card gains 200 ATK for each "Gravekeeper's" monster in your Graveyard. If this face-up card would be destroyed, you can discard 1 "Gravekeeper's" monster instead.

card_sets.set_name: Legendary Collection 4: Joey's World Mega Pack
